    NumericFunction1.DecimalFunction1, NumericFunction1.IntegralFunction1
    Enclosing class:
    NumericFunction1

    public abstract static class NumericFunction1.FlexFunction1
extends NumericFunction1
    The FlexFunction1 provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunction1. The only remaining methods that need to be implemented are the apply methods acting on longs and doubles. All apply calls using integer (in the generic sense) arguments will (by default) use the method acting on longs, and all calls using decimal arguments will use the method acting on doubles.
